Package: flash-termux
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Adinata (adivenxnataly)
Depends: android-tools, zstd, unzip, p7zip, tar, python
Recommends: unrar
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Advanced ROM flashing tool for Termux
 A comprehensive tool for extracting and flashing Android ROMs directly
 from Termux environment. Supports multiple archive formats and provides
 safety checks before flashing.
Homepage: https://github.com/adivenxnataly/flash-termux
